NAME

    UI::Notify::Cocoa - Posts a Cocoa Notification

SYNOPSIS

        use UI::Notify::Cocoa;
    
        UI::Notify::Cocoa->show("Message");
        UI::Notify::Cocoa->show("Title", "Message");
        UI::Notify::Cocoa->show("Title", "Subtitle", "Message");

DESCRIPTION

    Displays a Cocoa Notification. Eventually will use XS but for now
    shells out to osascript. Module is OS X only.

GIT REPOSITORY

    http://github.com/athreef/UI-Notify-Cocoa

